data.description: This 1662 sq. ft. home features 3 bedrooms, and 2 bathrooms with a split floor plan with your owner's suite separate from the other sleeping areas. The home offers granite counters, breakfast bar/island, laundry room with storage cabinets. In the master bedroom, you will find the walk-in closet, full master bathroom features dual sinks and tub/shower. The backyard has room to pursue any additions! Two car garage. Schedule a showing today and experience the warmth and comfort it has to offer.
